    <tag>intersection</tag><text>$</text>AB <text>$</text>CD<tag>/intersection</tag>
  <tag>/point</tag>
<tag>/graph</tag>
<tag>p</tag>Note, Doenet now returns the shared equation for the line,<tag>/p</tag>
